description: Lists all supported versions for Snow on-device services. Returns an array of ServiceVersion object containing the supported versions for a particular service.

parameters.name: ServiceName
parameters.description: The name of the service for which you're requesting supported versions.

parameters.name: DependentServices
parameters.description: A list of names and versions of dependant services of the requested service. (dict) --- The name and version of the service dependant on the requested service. ServiceName (string) --- The name of the dependent service. ServiceVersion (dict) --- The version of the dependent service. Version (string) --- The version number of the requested service.

nested_params.name: ServiceName
nested_params.description: The name of the dependent service.

nested_params.name: ServiceVersion
nested_params.description: The version of the dependent service.

nested_params.name: Version
nested_params.description: The version number of the requested service.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The version number of the requested service.
